spells.description: While this item is in your bags, equipped, or being used for transmog you will occasionally be consumed by the curse.

description: Ancient runes decorate the metal head and trail onto the handle in the form of carved etchings. These patterns become more erratic as they reach the pommel, eventually becoming nothing more than frantic scratches.
